(firstQuint)Effect of Artronat on the Quality of Life of Patient With Osteoarthritis.

 Osteoarthritis is a degenerative disease that greatly impairs the quality of life of patients.

 A nutritional supplement may help, in association with the normal treatment of osteoarthritis, improving the quality of life of such patients, in reducing pain and/or improving join flexibility.

